show.description: When Ananya Rathore returns from the dead to reclaim her legacy, she must outwit power-hungry rivals, face her treacherous uncle Dinesh, and spar with her dangerous yet magnetic husband Rudra in a game where love, revenge, and survival collide. Watch Now!
